Class Secret

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.azure.security.keyvault.secrets.models.SecretBase
      • com.azure.security.keyvault.secrets.models.Secret

  • public class Secret
extends SecretBase
    Secret is the resource consisting of name, value and its attributes inherited from SecretBase. It is managed by Secret Service.
    See Also:
    SecretClient, SecretAsyncClient
